title: Cape Lookout National Seashore: Lighthouse
body: Lighthouse Photos                    Cape Lookout Lighthouse   13 Photos  Photos of the 1859 lighthouse, light apparatus, the buildings of the light station complex, and other related images.          Lighthouse at Night   4 Photos  In celebration of the 150th anniversary of the completion of the second Cape Lookout lighthouse, the tower was illuminated at night for a month prior to the anniversary.          Lighthouse Anniversary Celebration   3 Photos  On November 1, 2009, Cape Lookout National Seashore and hundreds of friends and partners celebrated the 150th anniversary of the first lighting of Cape Lookout's second lighthouse.
